 and weigh sugar into it. Sprinkle sugar evenly over prepared baking tray and bake for 6-8 minutes (220°C), or until amber in colour. Remove from oven and immediately sprinkle with pistachios and thyme. Set aside to cool completely (approx. 10 minutes)."},{"content":"Break praline into shards. Place half of the praline into mixing bowl and mill <b>5 sec\/speed 7<b>."},{"content":"Place milled praline onto a serving plate and unmould ice cream torte on top of it. Decorate with remaining praline shards and raspberries. Serve immediately."}],"hintsAndTricks":["You can also use a silicone cake tin (omit lining with plastic wrap) to make unmoulding easier."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","48h 40m","6 portions"]}